* Temporal vs\nSCD Type 2
** SCD Type 2
***_ Business/analytical purpose
***_ Track customer/product/entity changes
***_ Attribute sales to historical location
***_ Explicit business-meaningful versions
** Temporal (History) Tables
***_ Technical/operational purpose
***_ Debug data ingestion issues
***_ Compliance & audit trails
***_ Reproduce reports from past
***_ Track load times / source files
** Both Use Validity Dates
***_ SCD Type 2: business validity
***_ Temporal: technical timestamps
@endmindmap
